1993;;The Silver Brumby;;Australian;;John Tatoulis;;Russell Crowe, Caroline Goodall;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Silver_Brumby_(1993_film);;A mother tells her daughter a fable about the prince of the brumbies- brumby being a term for the feral horses of Australia- who must find his place amongst his kind, while avoiding The Man who always seems to be hunting him.